title: Bunkercast XXIII: Around the AFC in 32 minutes
itunes:title: Bunkercast XXIII: Around the AFC in 32 minutes
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal go around the AFC in 32 minutes. With only 2 minutes allowed per team, the heroes quickly take you through each team and where they should be looking to fill their holes with draft needs.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
